two_party_helpers.notes:
The primary driver for Ut, Sc, As, Un, Dt in S6 Commands. TaskEvent shape for each verb:
- task.created: { type, task: { id, title, description, status, assignee, createdBy, createdAt, updatedAt } }
- task.updated: { type, taskId, changes: Partial<{title, description}>, updatedAt, updatedBy }
- task.status_changed: { type, taskId, status: 'open'|'in_progress'|'done'|'cancelled', updatedAt, updatedBy }
- task.assigned: { type, taskId, assignee: string|null, updatedAt, updatedBy }
- task.deleted: { type, taskId, updatedAt, updatedBy }
